# Competitor Analysis — Airalo & EIOTCLUB

Compiled: 2026-04-24. Sources: live crawl of 25+ pages on both sites + mobile screenshots.
Use this when Jordan asks about the front page, shop layout, what Evair is missing, or
any UX/product decision that competitors already solved.

## Quick positioning map

| Brand | Market | Hero message | Price signal | Primary audience |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **Airalo** | Global travel eSIM | "Feel the freedom of unlimited data" (mobile) / "A better way to stay connected" (desktop) | "From $4.00" in every country tile | International travelers |
| **EIOTCLUB** | IoT SIM + travel eSIM | "Experience Seamless Connectivity" | "$1.00 Trial plan" on home | IoT/security-camera/trail-cam owners + travelers |
| **Evair** (today) | eSIM + USA physical SIM | Varies | Cheapest physical ~$8.99 | Unclear — mixed |

## PART 1 — AIRALO (www.airalo.com)

Tech: Nuxt/Vue + PrimeVue SPA. Theme color `#85CCDB`. No public `/login /signup /cart` URLs
(modal-only, tighter funnel).

### Site tree
- `/` — home
- `/{country}-esim` — country pages (e.g. `/united-states-esim`, `/japan-esim`)
- `/how-airalo-works` — sectioned explainer (4 anchor-tab sections)
- `/how-airalo-works/what-is-an-esim` — 4 short paragraphs defining eSIM
- `/how-airalo-works/device-compatibility` — compatibility rules + FAQ
- `/help` — 3 categories, ~90 articles (Getting Started / My Account & Airmoney / Using & Managing eSIMs)
- `/blog` — Magazine (long-form travel guides, 10–26 min reads)
- `/more-info/contact` — minimal, pushes everyone to live chat

### Country-page template (memorize — this is the gold standard)
Order top to bottom:
1. H1 `{Country} eSIMs`
2. Country card with **named carrier chips** ("T-Mobile +1 other") + `Check compatibility` button
3. Microcopy: "If you're running low, you can always top up"
4. Microcopy: "The package starts when you connect to a supported network"
5. Package-type tabs: `Data | Data/Calls/Texts | Standard | Unlimited`
6. **Package grid** = validity (3d/7d/15d/30d) × data (1/3/5/10/20/50GB). US example: 3d 1GB $4, 30d 50GB $42
7. Cross-sell: "Need broader coverage?" → Regional + Global
8. Social proof: "Why do over 20 million people choose Airalo?"
9. 4-question FAQ (install timing, how to use, reuse, renewals)
10. 24/7 support card
11. 3 embedded explainer videos ("Learn with Airalo")
12. App install banner with App Store 4.7 / Google Play 4.6 star ratings

### Hidden concepts (found in help center)
- **Airmoney** = prepaid wallet (referral $3/referral, birthday bonus, loyalty)
- **Loyalty Program** = tier system
- **Discover+ Global eSIM** = subscription global product
- **Renewals** = auto-topup when 10% data remaining
- **eSIM recycling** = reuse old eSIM for new trip
- **Trusted devices** = device-based security (no 2FA needed)
- **China VPN guide** = they publish SEO answers to market-specific friction

### Airalo signature moves
1. Search-first hero: "Where do you need an eSIM?" — sticky on mobile
2. Mobile hero copy ≠ desktop copy (deliberately different voice)
3. Illustrated human hero (not product render)
4. iOS Smart App Banner + inline "Download the app" banner stacked
5. Color-zoned scrolling sections (teal → green → etc.)
6. Single-column country list on mobile, full-width pills
7. "Regional" and "Global" eSIM tiers (cross-country bundles)
8. Modal-only auth (no standalone URLs)
9. Embedded explainer videos on every country page
10. Floating orange chat bubble always visible

## PART 2 — EIOTCLUB (www.eiotclub.com)

Tech: Shopify + Cloudflare. Sister domain `eiotclub.de` (EU/EUR). 20 currencies.

### Site tree
- `/` — home
- `/collections/all` — 86 products
- `/collections/sim-card` (travel SIMs), plus device/router/eSIM collections
- `/products/{slug}` — ~86 product detail pages
- `/pages/about-us` — product pitch + 4 named YouTuber testimonials
- `/pages/shipping-policy` — US + EU warehouse addresses published
- `/pages/refill` — links to `sim.eiotclub.com/eshop` ICCID refill portal
- `/pages/eiotclubcredits-rewards` — loyalty (10pts = $1, redeem for coupons OR products)
- `/policies/refund-policy` — extremely detailed, per-product
- `/policies/terms-of-service` — 29 sections, includes anti-LLM-training clause
- `/policies/privacy-policy` — thin, no GDPR even with EU store
- `/blogs/community` — 176 authored articles
- `/account/login` — simple, has inline FAQ about email verification
- Cart = **persistent slide-out on every page** with "Top Picks" cross-sell carousel

### Product-detail page template (memorize — it's deeper than Airalo)
1. Trust bar above fold: "Fast Shipping · 7-Day Returns · 10-Year Guarantee · 24/7 Service"
2. Long SEO title + review count linked to reviews section
3. 5-bullet benefit list
4. Urgency: "Black Friday ends Days ::" countdown
5. Network toggle: `Sim card | eSIM` tabs (same product, two delivery types)
6. **Plan cards in a grid**: plan name, carriers, network type, price, "🔥 Most Popular" badges
7. Dual CTA: `Add to cart | Shop Now`
8. Section nav tabs: `Overview | Advantages | Top-Up Options | FAQs | Reviews`
9. 6 H3 "Advantages" paragraphs (duplicated twice on page, intentional)
10. Device scenario icons + grid (Security / Tracker / Trail camera / Router)
11. **Product comparison table** (network bands, APN, country, cellular gen)
12. FAQs in tabs (About SIM card / About price)
13. 4 related blog posts
14. **Customer reviews with histogram** (87% 5-star, etc.) + merchant replies inline
15. "You may also like" — 6 related products
16. Persistent floating: `Live Chat | WhatsApp | FB Group | TOP`

### Cart (persistent on every page)
- "Members Get Priority Shipping" banner
- **"Top Picks" carousel** with 7 products + inline `+ ADD` (runs on every page)
- Trust row: Fast Shipping / 10-Yr Guarantee / 7-Day Returns / 24/7
- Order note + Apply (discount code)
- "Join Reward Program and Earn 2830 Points on this order" even when empty

### Rewards Program (EiotclubCredits)
- Sign up = 50 points instantly
- 10 points = $1 redemption
- Earn: per $1 spent + birthday +30 + Facebook share +10 + like +10
- Redeem as 75/150/200/250-point coupons OR whole products (Europe SIM 200 pts, USA 4G 250 pts)
- Max 1 redemption per 7 days

### Refill portal
- External app at `sim.eiotclub.com/eshop/`
- Enter ICCID → check status → top up
- Auto-renewal toggle
- **Shared plan**: one plan across multiple SIMs (e.g. 3 "card lines")
- 14 payment methods listed (Amex, Discover, Diners, MC, Visa, Link, Apple Pay, Google Pay,
  Bancontact, EPS, iDEAL, Przelewy24, Cartes Bancaires, PayPal)

### EIOTCLUB signature moves
1. Persistent slide-out cart with upsells on EVERY page
2. Per-product UGC reviews with histogram + merchant replies
3. "Hot 10375 Sold" sales-count social proof
4. Product comparison tables with technical specs (bands, APN)
5. Loyalty program redeemable for actual products
6. External ICCID-based refill webapp (no account needed)
7. Shared-plan multi-SIM pooling
8. 10-year warranty on hardware
9. Published warehouse addresses (US + Germany)
10. 3 support channels: Live Chat + WhatsApp + FB Group
11. Authored blog with expert-byline bios + photos (Dr. Marcus Chen, Sarah Vance)
12. Countdown urgency ("Black Friday ends")
13. Sister country domain (eiotclub.de for EUR)

